{"tid":839541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[點解要當香港人係水魚] 耗資60億英鎊沙特高鐵啟用　全程450公里　期望年載6000萬人次","createTime":"2018-09-28T04:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T09:40:54.000Z","uid":195944,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eb079721218fa807b0c9e6f24e424b544cbdada5","tid":839541,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"沙特阿拉伯哈拉曼高速鐵路（Haramain High Speed Rail）耗資達60億英鎊（<span style=\"color: red;\">約615億港元</span>），日前（25日）舉行啟用儀式。國王薩勒曼（King Salman）雖已年過八旬，當日亦出席並視察各項設施。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，鐵路全程<span style=\"color: red;\">450公里</span>，連接聖城麥卡（Mecca）和麥地那（Medina），沿途有三個中途站，<span style=\"color: red;\">列車最高時速可達每小時360公里</span>。目前沙特交通主要依賴陸路，預料通車後，往返上述兩個城市行車時間，<span style=\"color: red;\">將由4個小時縮短到2個小時</span>。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，乘搭高鐵的乘客，主要是前往朝覲的穆斯林信徙及一般遊客，期望<span style=\"color: red;\">每年載客量可以達6000萬人次</span>。當地官員形容，這是中東最大型交通計畫。鐵路將於下星期正式開放公眾使用。<br />\n<br />\n新華社報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">中鐵十八局集團和中土集團</span>，分別參與鐵路項目不同標段建設，並是中國企業在海外參建的世界首條穿越沙漠地帶高鐵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180927/s00005/1538060940604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180927%2Fs00005%2F1538060940604&d=35VR44aBLSg6O01mXEyuI%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c9f6d508\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180927%2Fs00005%2F1538060940604&h=2e628ccd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180927/s00005/1538060940604</a><br />\n<br />\n同樣有大陸參與<br />\n一條就26公里844億 一條450公里615億<br />\n一條時速唔過300km/h 一條就最高360km/h<br />\n一條就慳到30分鐘到廣州 一條到第二個城市就慳兩個鐘<br />\n一條載客量就預2900萬 一條就6000萬<br />\n<br />\n點解要當我地係水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddf0e05c383b3d855e6ad7a302450a445ce7b0f","tid":839541,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:27:32.000Z","msg":"連接聖城麥卡（Mecca）和麥地那（Medina）<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47edbcccc768349c56af8e6c1dd29b5ccc3402e7","tid":839541,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"理撚得你，錢已袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fda853b09b13cc589a476bac2efd20708d9a0d","tid":839541,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eddf0e05c383b3d855e6ad7a302450a445ce7b0f","tid":839541,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:27:32.000Z","msg":"連接聖城麥卡（Mecca）和麥地那（Medina）<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"唔係好多人去呢兩個地方咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9461aa587684253af7fd86044064044793aa392","tid":839541,"uid":42042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65fda853b09b13cc589a476bac2efd20708d9a0d","tid":839541,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eddf0e05c383b3d855e6ad7a302450a445ce7b0f","tid":839541,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:27:32.000Z","msg":"連接聖城麥卡（Mecca）和麥地那（Medina）<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />